data.description: Welcome to 23506 Canyon Lake Drive N, a picturesque oasis nestled within the coveted private gated community of Canyon Lake, California. This stunning single-story, single-family home boasts a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom layout, offering an idyllic retreat for you and your loved ones. As you approach this charming residence, you'll be captivated by its curb appeal, featuring a manicured front yard and a welcoming facade. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by an inviting 1342 square feet of comfortable living space that exudes warmth and character. The heart of the home is the spacious living area, which seamlessly connects to the Kitchen, creating an open and airy ambiance. Large windows throughout the house flood the interior with natural light, creating a bright and cheerful atmosphere. The well-appointed kitchen offers ample counter and cabinet space, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining guests. The master bedroom is a peaceful retreat, featuring an ensuite bathroom for added convenience, as well as a sliding glass door for easy back patio access. Two additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family members or guests, each with its own unique charm. The second bathroom is tastefully designed and serves the needs of the household. One of the standout features of this home is its expansive pool sized backyard, a private sanctuary where you can relax, entertain, and enjoy the beautiful California weather. Whether you're hosting a barbecue with friends, playing catch with the kids, or simply unwinding under the shade of mature trees, this backyard is the perfect outdoor escape. Canyon Lake itself offers an array of amenities, including boating, fishing, golfing, and access to a clubhouse with a restaurant, pool, and tennis courts. This community provides a unique and serene lifestyle, where you can enjoy the best of both relaxation and recreation. With its ideal single-story layout, spacious backyard, and a prime location in the private, gated community of Canyon Lake, 23506 Canyon Lake Drive N is the epitome of California living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home your own and start enjoying the Canyon Lake lifestyle today. Contact us for a private tour soon before it's gone!
